"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/519020","Ministry of Defence","false","2016-05-24","<p>140 UK military personnel and four RAF Typhoon aircraft are currently deployed on NATO's Baltic Air Policing mission.</p><p> </p>","Canterbury","Mr Julian Brazier",,"2016-05-24T15:10:09.213Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/519020/answer","Biography information for Sir Julian Brazier","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/519020/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/519020/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2016-05-18","Armed Forces: Baltic States","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, how many (a) UK military personnel and (b) RAF Typhoons are currently deployed on NATO's Baltic air policing mission.","false","Biography information for Emily Thornberry","Islington South and Finsbury","Emily Thornberry","37340"
